    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【游戏直播・配信OK】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Slot &amp; Dungeons》可以自由进行直播和配信，任何人都可以。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行直播或配信时，无需获得许可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果能在Steam评论或官方Discord上分享您的感想，我们将不胜感激！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >什么是老虎机与地下城？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/bbadd0028e376876b804c4b01df9cae5.poster.avif?t=1760945354\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/bbadd0028e376876b804c4b01df9cae5.webm?t=1760945354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/bbadd0028e376876b804c4b01df9cae5.mp4?t=1760945354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Slot &amp; Dungeons》是一款单人卡组构筑类Roguelike游戏。游戏中，敌人和掉落物品的位置会随轮盘结果随机变化。 使用你的技能打倒敌人，升级强化，努力突破地牢吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用 “符号” 来建造插槽</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/a85c4e75919df23abcb559aa7668a240.poster.avif?t=1760945354\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/a85c4e75919df23abcb559aa7668a240.webm?t=1760945354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/a85c4e75919df23abcb559aa7668a240.mp4?t=1760945354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿途的敌人和征服地牢所需的资源都会以 “符号” 的形式融入插槽中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符号可以在穿越每一层时获得，也可以从楼层内的各种效果中获得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符号还可用于地牢中的各种效果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>符号</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>咒语</strong>：这些咒语在抽取插槽后生效，并在楼层中产生各种效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物品</strong>：物品放置在地板上的方格中，当您拾取或靠近它们时会产生效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌人</strong>：他们是追杀你的人。 查看每个人的特征，为你的攻击寻找线索！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/b2560af2a982e23d1186e2597c86301d.poster.avif?t=1760945354\" width=630 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/b2560af2a982e23d1186e2597c86301d.webm?t=1760945354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224750/extras/b2560af2a982e23d1186e2597c86301d.mp4?t=1760945354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《老虎机与地下城》中，您可以从几个角色中选择一个来接受地下城的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有不同的能力和标志，例如战士擅长高耐久和近战攻击，法师擅长法术型歼灭。</p>",
